      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in the ASTM F1717 standard and the FDA guidance for spinal implant mechanical testing. These QoIs directly inform the regulatory decision on construct mechanical adequacy. Relevance is high."
